<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/27001AHPHSDCGHGCCRQCHCPMCLLSSSQJG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Crisprr + Rusty Crows Double Bill: Live Rock and Roll at its Best";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Rock the Weekend: One Night, Two Epic Bands.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Experience it Live!</span> A high voltage double header featuring two of the best bands the BC Interior has to offer: <span class=\"BoldText\">Rusty Crows</span> and <span class=\"BoldText\">Crisprr</span>. Friday, March 20, 2026 Creekside Theatre, Kelowna<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">🎸 Feel the Energy of Rusty Crows<span><br/></span></span>One of the Okanagan’s top live party bands, Rusty Crows deliver authentic, high-energy performances packed with fan favorites from Foo Fighters, Pearl Jam, The Tragically Hip, and more. This is a band built to move a crowd.<span><br/></span>Rusty Crows’ website: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://rustycrows.weebly.com/\">rustycrows.weebly.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">🔥 Catch Crisprr’s Final Local Show Before They Blow Up<span><br/></span></span>Fresh out of the studio, they will be playing brand-new tracks from their upcoming album plus the classic rock anthems you love. Their latest release, Snow Is Falling, has landed in the top 15% of <span class=\"BoldText\">global Spotify streams</span> for 2025 releases. This is your <span class=\"BoldText\">last chance</span> to see them live before they hit the road for an 8-city West Coast tour with Montreal’s acclaimed Led Zeppelin tribute band <span class=\"ItalicText\">Black Dog</span>. Come discover why Kelowna voted them <span class=\"BoldText\">2025’s favorite band</span>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Crisprr’s website: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://crisprr.ca/\">Crisprr.ca</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">📅 Friday Night. One Unforgettable Show.</span><span><br/></span>Two powerhouse bands. One night of pure rock.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">✅ Secure your tickets now</span>—before they’re gone.<span><br/></span>This double header is set to sell out. Don’t miss your chance to be part of Kelowna’s biggest rock moment of the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Rock hard. Live loud.</span> 🤘
""";
