	<span class=\"BoldText\">Red Section (First 3 rows)</span><span><br/></span>$33.00 All Ages<span><br/></span>No Discount Codes available for this section<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Green Section - Rows D - M & AA - CC</span><span><br/></span>$73.50 Adult<span><br/></span>$66.00 Senior 65+<span><br/></span>$39.75 Student (19 & Under)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Yellow Section - Rows N - P & Balcony</span><span><br/></span>$68.25 Adult<span><br/></span>$60.00 Senior 65+<span><br/></span>$33.25 Student (19 & Under)<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All Prices Include all Fees & Taxes</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Back by popular demand, The Gary Cable Project returns with Legendary Rock Live!, a celebration of the greatest music ever made -- Chicago, Lighthouse, Supertramp, Steely Dan, Toto, Billy Joel, Elton John, Earth Wind & Fire -- and more! With Special Musical Guests<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Proceeds support Community Foundation of the North Okanagan</span>
""";
