  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$49.00 Per Person</span><span><br/></span>Includes fees & taxes<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A Western Canadian Music “Entertainer of the Year”, VDPAC favourite, and much-loved, globe-trotting multi-award nominee, master pianist and songwriter, <span class=\"BoldText\">Michael Kaeshammer</span> returns with his band to dazzle and delight his many fans.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Michael’s superb 15th album, <span class=\"BoldText\">Turn It Up</span> is broadly described as “eclectic yet accessible jazz-based pop” but more expansive than one simple description - including his audacious treatment of the beloved Queen classic “Crazy Little Thing Called Love” - a bass-boosted anthem that positively soars!
""";
