<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/35201AQQRSLKMCNNBJNMJCGMJTGPJQHBV> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Okanagan Ukrainian Festival";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$33.50 - Adult<span><br/></span>$28.50 - Senior 60+/Students<span><br/></span>$18.25 - Children under 12</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Includes fees and taxes</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">OKANAGAN UKRAINIAN FESTIVAL CELEBRATES 26 YEARS!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">The Sadok Ukrainian Dance Ensemble</span> invites all to the <span class=\"BoldText\">THE OKANAGAN UKRAINIAN FESTIVAL </span>on Sunday, May 24th at 2:00pm at the Vernon Performing Arts Centre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This year, Sadok celebrates 26 Years of sharing their Ukrainian Canadian culture with the World with special guests Pokotillo Ukrainian Dancers of Kamloops.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Sadok Ukrainian Dance Ensemble is a local dance theatre troupe that continually pushes the boundaries of this unique art form by entertaining and educating their audience about their beautiful Ukrainian Canadian Heritage. They have performed throughout Okanagan Valley, Vancouver, Alberta and Los Angeles, California. They performed at Disneyland, California where they shared their culture with the world. Their travels have taken them on three occasions to Ukraine to study dance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is the 31st theatrical dance and music production choreographed by Artistic Director, Andrea Malysh.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Sadok is vibrant and colourful!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come for an afternoon of Ukrainian Dance, Music and Ukrainian Canadian Spirit!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For More info on Sadok:<span><br/></span>Call Andrea Malysh (250) 309-6948<span><br/></span>Visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.sadok.net/\">www.sadok.net</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Okanagan Ukrainian Festival Celebrates 26 Years!
""";
