<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/31401ACGSQBSNGJMMSMSJDBKPVTCCSKMC> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Music of Lion King - In Concert";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$99.75 - Rows A – C<span><br/></span>$89.75 - Rows D – J and AA to CC<span><br/></span>$79.75 - Rows K – P<span><br/></span></span><span class=\"BoldText\">$69.75 - Rows DD – KK</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Immerse yourself in the unforgettable music of The Lion King in a spectacular live concert event! From the heartfelt \"Can You Feel the Love Tonight\" to the joyous \"Hakuna Matata\", and the powerful \"Circle of Life\" by Elton John, this is a celebration of one of Disney’s most iconic stories.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Presented by star soloists from the original Broadway productions and performed by the renowned Broadway Symphonic Orchestra & Choir, this concert captures the magic, adventure, and spirit of the Pride Lands. Experience the Magic of Africa and the timeless music that has inspired generations.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get your tickets now and be part of this extraordinary journey into the heart of the savanna.
""";
