<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/5399ASDTMRPPLKPSQKCKBDRVNJGKJRDRS> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Woodshed (John Wort Hannam & T. Buckley)";
  schema:description """
	$40.00 Per Person (<span class=\"BoldText\">No Minors 19+</span>)<span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Acclaimed roots songwriters John Wort Hannam and T. Buckley make up the woodshed, a modern folk duo based in Alberta, whose name refers to the beginning of Buckley and Hannam’s collaboration - woodshedding songs together during a residency at the Banff Centre for arts and creativity in 2017.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>After a captivating performance at the 2023 Canadian folk music awards, Buckley and Hannam finally decided to ratify their collaboration and bring the woodshed to life. Together they bring a beautiful vocal blend of brotherly harmonies combined with gutsy and sophisticated song writing alongside intricate guitar playing.
""";
