<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/36601ATRPSQKSGHPQNCLQHVKLVNDQQCLK> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "This Is The Moment!";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$20.00 Adult<span><br/></span>(16 and under are free and do not need a ticket)</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Vernon Community Singers is Vernon’s largest choir with 83 men and women who sing for the pure joy of singing in harmony.  The Musical Director is Paul Hunter who started the choir 32 years ago as an inclusive community group for people who love singing. His creative and knowledgeable direction molds this powerful group of voices to create beautiful harmonies and musical moments.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The song that inspired the title of the concert, ‘This Is The Moment’ describes a crucial turning point when a person casts away all doubts and moves into the future. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>‘Do You Hear The People Sing?’ asks us to realize that this is the moment to create hope.  Our program presents different reasons and ways to have hope in this future.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We will be singing songs from Jazz, Pop, Folk, Gospels and Africa that will make you want to sway to the harmonies and tap your feet to the fun arrangements! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We are excited to have the flute trio, The Passion Flutes as our guest performers and  are happy to have Julie Wormald as our talented accompanist again<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our Choir has been supporting Music Education in Vernon for 32 years with part of the concert proceeds always going to various School District 22 music programs.  We invite you to come enjoy the concert of the season while helping this worthy cause!
""";
